column2: Dr. Ing. h.c. F. Porsche AG
column4: Dr. Ing. h.c. F. Porsche AG engages in automotive and financial services business in Germany, Europe, North America, China, and internationally. The company engages in the development, manufacturing, and sale of vehicles, as well as provision of related services. It also offers customer and dealer financing, leasing, and mobility and other finance-related services. The company was formerly known as Porsche Fünfte Vermögensverwaltung AG and changed its name to Dr. Ing. h.c. F. Porsche AG in November 2009. The company was incorporated in 2009 and is headquartered in Stuttgart, Germany. Dr. Ing. h.c. F. Porsche AG operates as a subsidiary of Porsche Holding Stuttgart GmbH.
